    "description": {
      "value": "<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\">Prerequisite: Level 2+ Warlock, Warlock cantrip that deals damage or Eldritch Blast feature</span></p></blockquote><p>Choose one of your Warlock cantrips that deals damage or your Eldritch Blast feature. You can add your Charisma modifier to that spell or your Eldritch Blast's damage rolls.</p><p><strong>Repeatable.</strong> You can gain this invocation more than once. Each time you do so, choose a different eligible cantrip.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-Uz4mskdq5tR4Ql7K\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The change to your cantrip will have to be made manually by adding \"@abilities.cha.mod\" to the \"Bonus\" field of your spell's damage.</p></section>",
